MAOSの暴走により、大混乱となっていた。\r\nしかし、天野美雪や島本和子らスタッフ必死の復旧作業により、混乱は収まり、システムも正常化した。\r\n\r\n一方、混乱に乗じて井上雅和は宮下たまみをドラクル城に監禁し、陵辱の限りをつくしていた。\r\nそして、二人の前に、北沢牧子が現れ、自ら進んで、たまみの身代わりに……。"}],"crt":[{"id":101446,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/4e/17/101446_crt_7Wg6e.jpg","name":"北沢牧子","desc":"主角"},{"id":101447,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/5f/61/101447_crt_i7A5k.jpg","name":"神崎志津子","desc":"客串"},{"id":101448,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/f0/86/101448_crt_34qjq.jpg","name":"笹塚京","desc":"主角"},{"id":101449,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/fc/3f/101449_crt_5x6F8.jpg","name":"島本和子","desc":"主角"},{"id":101450,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/e6/f2/101450_crt_I7GgJ.jpg","name":"日泉ひかる","desc":"客串"},{"id":101451,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/c2/60/101451_crt_xL1jz.jpg","name":"宮下たまみ","desc":"主角"},{"id":101452,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/de/2e/101452_crt_Y9ASZ.jpg","name":"緑川さくら","desc":"配角"},{"id":101453,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/7e/c6/101453_crt_80N22.jpg","name":"佐久間由佳里","desc":"配角"},{"id":101454,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/b7/56/101454_crt_09DXc.jpg","name":"天野美雪","desc":"主角"},{"id":101455,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/a7/18/101455_crt_9S3xy.jpg","name":"胡桃沢裕子","desc":"配角"},{"id":101479,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/de/52/101479_crt_9luX4.jpg","name":"財前瑠璃子","desc":"配角"},{"id":101480,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/c0/4a/101480_crt_QN6a0.jpg","name":"森本弘美","desc":"配角"},{"id":101483,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/4c/66/101483_crt_4YaxP.jpg","name":"井上雅和","desc":"配角"},{"id":101484,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/12/98/101484_crt_cctP7.jpg","name":"梶原まこと","desc":"配角"},{"id":101486,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/e2/aa/101486_crt_SCSSV.jpg","name":"江頭善司","desc":"配角"},{"id":101487,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/d9/4d/101487_crt_WZani.jpg","name":"劉角凡","desc":"客串"},{"id":101488,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/7a/b1/101488_crt_rs81r.jpg","name":"佐渡島慈吾郎","desc":"配角"},{"id":101489,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/76/27/101489_crt_t9xR8.jpg","name":"服部友蔵","desc":"配角"}